'''霍華德·布魯斯·蘇特'''（{{lang-en|Howard Bruce Sutter}}，{{bd|1953年|1月8日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，生涯曾效力過小熊、紅雀和勇士等隊。蘇特是大聯盟1970年代至1980年間最有壓制力的後援投手，他生涯一共入選6次明星賽，拿過一次世界大賽冠軍。生涯防禦率2.82，並拿下300次救援成功，在當時是史上第三多。他不僅在1979年拿下國聯賽揚獎，並且仍是目前國聯唯一一位拿過5次聯盟救援王的投手。

2006年，蘇特入選名人堂。同年紅雀隊將他的42號背號退休，並在2014年將他引薦至紅雀隊名人堂。而他曾在費城人隊的小聯盟球隊擔任過顧問。
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥小熊===
1976年5月，蘇特加入小熊隊。該年他拿下6勝3敗，10次救援成功。隔年他的防禦率只有1.34，並順利入選明星賽。而他也順利在賽揚獎及MVP票選上分別拿下第6和第7名。<ref name=BR>{{cite web|title=Bruce Sutter Statistics and History|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/suttebr01.shtml|publisher=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=2014-04-07|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716020031/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/suttebr01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1977年9月8日，蘇特達成了罕見的完美一局（1局投球僅用9顆球便三振3名打者）。

1978年，雖然蘇特的防禦率上升到3.19，不過他拿下27次救援成功。<ref name=BR/>1979年5月，小熊隊交易來後援投手Dick Tidrow。受惠於Tidrow的表現，讓蘇特累積了不少救援成功。<ref name=Fimaite>{{cite news|last1=Fimaite|first1=Ron|title=This pitch in time saves nine|url=https://www.si.com/vault/1979/09/17/823981/this-pitch-in-time-saves-nine-when-chicago-requires-late-inning-help-out-of-the-bullpen-comes-bruce-sutter-whose-unique-quotsplit-fingered-fastballquot-has-made-him-the-most-effective-relief-pitcher-in-the-game|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|date=1979-09-17|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022223642/https://www.si.com/vault/1979/09/17/823981/this-pitch-in-time-saves-nine-when-chicago-requires-late-inning-help-out-of-the-bullpen-comes-bruce-sutter-whose-unique-quotsplit-fingered-fastballquot-has-made-him-the-most-effective-relief-pitcher-in-the-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他以37次救援成功追平國聯紀錄，並拿下國聯賽揚獎。1980年，他再度以28次救援成功領先全聯盟。整年他拿下5勝8敗，防禦率2.64，不過他的三振數也首次低於100次。<ref name=BR/>
===聖路易紅雀===
1980年12月，小熊隊將蘇特交易至紅雀，換來Leon Durham、Ken Reitz和一名日後指定球員。1981年，他整年拿下25次救援成功，防禦率為2.62。<ref name=BR/>不僅連續5年入選明星賽，還在賽揚獎票選上拿下第五名。<ref name=BR/>

1982年，蘇特拿下36次救援成功，並在賽揚獎票選上拿下第三名。<ref name=BR/>這年紅雀也順利拿下世界大賽冠軍，而蘇特在世界大賽上拿下2次救援成功。1983年，蘇特拿下9勝10敗，防禦率為4.23。<ref name=BR/>雖然他只拿下21次救援成功，不過他在這年締造一個罕見的獨力牽制。當時蘇特在投球時，海盜隊跑者Bill Madlock因離壘過遠受到一壘手[[基斯·赫南德茲|基斯·赫南德茲]]的注意，結果蘇特發現後直接自行衝下丘往一壘方向觸殺Madlock。<ref name=Mulligan>{{cite book|last1=Mulligan|first1=Stephen|title=Were You There?: Over 300 Wonderful, Weird, and Wacky Moments from Pittsburgh's Three Rivers Stadium|date=2013|publisher=[[Dorrance_Publishing_Co.|Dorrance Publishing Co.]]|isbn=978-1480905023|page=131|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rzP9vlQFkIkC|access-date=2014-07-20|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411023648/https://books.google.com/books?id=rzP9vlQFkIkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1981年至1984年間，蘇特拿下3次年度救援投手獎。其中1984年他更是以45次救援成功一度寫下國聯新紀錄。<ref name=Kurkjian>{{cite web|last1=Kurkjian|first1=Tim|title=Mastery of splitter led to Sutter's success|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/columns/story?id=2531648|website=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|access-date=2014-07-20|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408213216/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/columns/story?id=2531648|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===亞特蘭大勇士===
1984年12月，蘇特以自由球員身分加盟勇士隊。而蘇特表示他是因為敬佩透納廣播公司老闆[[泰德·透納|泰德·透納]]和勇士強打者[[戴爾·墨菲|戴爾·墨菲]]才選擇加入勇士隊的。<ref name=NYBrave>{{cite news|title=Sutter becomes a Brave|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1984/12/08/sports/sutter-becomes-a-brave-atlanta-dec-7-ap-bruce-sutter-a-free-agent-relief-pitcher.html|access-date=2014-07-04|agency=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1984-12-08|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713103714/http://www.nytimes.com/1984/12/08/sports/sutter-becomes-a-brave-atlanta-dec-7-ap-bruce-sutter-a-free-agent-relief-pitcher.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而紅雀隊總教練也坦承球隊在沒有蘇特的情況會打得很掙扎。<ref name=Durso>{{cite news|last1=Durso|first1=Joseph|title=Sutter-less Cards optimistic|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/04/sports/sutter-less-cards-optimistic.html?module=Search&mabReward=relbias%3Aw|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1985-03-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411023650/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/04/sports/sutter-less-cards-optimistic.html?module=Search&mabReward=relbias:w|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1984年，勇士隊全隊只拿下49次救援成功，而蘇特一人光是在紅雀就拿下45次救援成功。<ref name=Marriage>{{cite news|last1=Martinez|first1=Michael|title=Sutter and Braves: A happy marriage|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/31/sports/sutter-and-braves-a-happy-marriage.html|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1985-03-31|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411023652/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/03/31/sports/sutter-and-braves-a-happy-marriage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而蘇特來到勇士隊後防禦率上升到4.48，只拿下23次救援成功。<ref name=BR/>更糟的是，他在球季結束後肩膀受了傷。<ref name=Tribune87>{{cite news|title=Atlanta Braves relief pitcher Bruce Sutter plans to...|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-01-23/sports/8701060551_1_contract-al-pitcher-outfielder-max-venable|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=1987-01-23|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714201814/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-01-23/sports/8701060551_1_contract-al-pitcher-outfielder-max-venable|dead-url=no}}</ref>1986年3月，他短暫在春訓亮相後，便動了肩膀手術。<ref name=Robb>{{cite news|last1=Robb|first1=Sharon|title=Atlanta's fireman off to a hot start: Braves relieved after Sutter's first outing|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1986-03-12/sports/8601150396_1_first-pitch-braves-bruce-sutter|access-date=2014-07-05|work=[[Sun-Sentinel|Sun-Sentinel]]|date=1986-03-12|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714224603/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1986-03-12/sports/8601150396_1_first-pitch-braves-bruce-sutter|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月，蘇特表示他的球速比起前幾年已有快速下滑。<ref name=Slow>{{cite news|last1=Verrell|first1=Gordon|title=Sutter's comeback goes slow: Braves relief ace's velocity in question|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1986-03-30/sports/0210160121_1_bruce-sutter-inning-angeles-dodgers|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[Orlando_Sentinel|Orlando Sentinel]]|date=1986-03-30|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230925/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1986-03-30/sports/0210160121_1_bruce-sutter-inning-angeles-dodgers|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他拿下2勝，防禦率4.34。<ref name=BR/>7月31日，球隊總教練更是宣布蘇特的球季直接提前結束。<ref name=Notebook>{{cite news|title=Wednesday's Notebook|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1986-07-31/sports/0240180132_1_arm-problems-sutter-arthrogram|access-date=2014-07-05|agency=[[Orlando_Sentinel|Orlando Sentinel]]|date=1986-07-31|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225743/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1986-07-31/sports/0240180132_1_arm-problems-sutter-arthrogram|dead-url=no}}</ref>1987年2月，蘇特再動了一次手術，導致他整季報銷。<ref name=Rome>{{cite news|title=Bruce Sutter recovering from surgery|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=348&dat=19870212&id=siBNAAAAIBAJ&pg=3097,2121973|access-date=2014-04-07|newspaper=[[Rome_News-Tribune|Rome News-Tribune]]|date=1987-02-12|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411023648/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=348&dat=19870212&id=siBNAAAAIBAJ&pg=3097,2121973|dead-url=no}}</ref>1988年，蘇特嘗試回歸球場，<ref name=PSU>{{cite web|last=Groff|first=Tyler|title=Bruce Sutter|url=http://pabook.libraries.psu.edu/palitmap/bios/Sutter__Bruce.html|publisher=Pennsylvania Center for the Book|access-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515225200/http://pabook.libraries.psu.edu/palitmap/bios/Sutter__Bruce.html#|archive-date=2013-05-15|url-status=dead}}</ref>但他只拿下1勝4敗，防禦率4.76。<ref name=BR/>最後他在球季結束後退休，並在9月進行右膝手術。<ref name=Knee>{{cite news|title=Sutter has surgery|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1988-09-27/sports/8802250647_1_padres-name-president-padres-game-dick-freeman|access-date=2014-07-19|work=Sun-Sentinel|date=1988-09-27|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729195433/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1988-09-27/sports/8802250647_1_padres-name-president-padres-game-dick-freeman|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==名人堂==
[[Image:CardsRetired42.PNG|thumb]]
2006年，蘇特在他的第13次名人堂票選中終於以400票，76.9%的得票率入選名人堂。他不僅是第四位入選名人堂的救援投手，更是第一位生涯完全沒有先發過的名人堂投手。<ref name=Leach>{{cite web|last=Leach|first=Matthew|title=Sutter braces for latest Hall chance|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20051220&content_id=1284771&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb&partnered=rss_mlb|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|access-date=2013-11-01|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103031744/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20051220&content_id=1284771&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb&partnered=rss_mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同年9月17日，紅雀隊將他的42號背號退休。他也成為[[傑基·羅賓森|傑基·羅賓森]]和[[馬里安諾·李維拉|馬里安諾·李維拉]]以外，唯一一位獲得42號背號退休的選手。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/NASApp/mlb/news/article.jsp?ymd=20060917&content_id=1668100&vkey=news_stl&fext=.jsp&c_id=stl |title=Cardinals pay tribute to Sutter | cardinals.com: News |website=St. Louis Cardinals|publisher=MLB|access-date=2014-04-07}}</ref>

2010年11月，他入選了紅雀隊名人堂。不過他因為妻子生病住院，而無法出席球隊名人堂獲獎典禮，因此讓前紅雀隊總教練Whitey Herzog代為領獎。<ref name=Subs>{{cite web|last1=Nelson|first1=Kathleen|title=Herzog subs for Sutter at Locker Room Luncheon|url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/other/herzog-subs-for-sutter-at-locker-room-luncheon/article_a483b694-1812-577e-a59c-0ef3af03b354.html|publisher=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]]|access-date=2014-07-05|date=2011-02-11|archive-date=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828162930/http://www.stltoday.com/sports/other/herzog-subs-for-sutter-at-locker-room-luncheon/article_a483b694-1812-577e-a59c-0ef3af03b354.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年1月，他和另外22名前紅雀隊選手們一同入選紅雀隊名人堂博物館。<ref>{{cite news |author=Cardinals Press Release |url=http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140118&content_id=66822534&vkey=pr_stl&c_id=stl |title=Cardinals establish Hall of Fame & detail induction process |publisher=www.stlouis.cardinals.[[MLB.com|mlb.com]] |date=2014-01-18 |access-date=2014-01-29 |archive-date=2014-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126165854/http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140118&content_id=66822534&vkey=pr_stl&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>
