==個人生活==
退休後，蘇特一家住在亞特蘭大。他的其中一個兒子查德是一名捕手，並曾在1999年大聯盟選秀會上被洋基隊選中。而查德只在小聯盟打了一年球就回到他的大學擔任教練。<ref name=Chad>{{cite web|title=Chad Sutter Bio|url=http://www.tulanegreenwave.com/sports/m-basebl/mtt/sutter_chad00.html|publisher=[[Tulane_University|Tulane University]]|access-date=2014-04-07|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907205942/http://www.tulanegreenwave.com/sports/m-basebl/mtt/sutter_chad00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2010年8月23日，蘇特受邀成為費城人隊小聯盟球隊的顧問。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100823&content_id=13826214&notebook_id=13827314&vkey=notebook_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi |title=Phillies bring in Sutter to mentor young arms | phillies.com: News |publisher=Philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com |access-date=2014-04-07 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104010426/http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100823&content_id=13826214&notebook_id=13827314&vkey=notebook_phi&c_id=phi&fext=.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在2A跟3A球隊裡協助發掘具有潛力的投手。<ref name=Stephens>{{cite web|last1=Stephens|first1=Bailey|title=Sutter to work with Phils' pitching prospects|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100823&content_id=13817022&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|access-date=2014-07-20|archive-date=2010-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825201135/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100823&content_id=13817022&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>
